{"tid":128381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「家居達人」家庭電器牌子","createTime":"2017-02-20T18:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T09:23:18.000Z","uid":30324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98ff5a5dd96c133df605416fc44faee552e42904","tid":128381,"uid":30324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:13:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我而家想買啲家庭電器，但又唔知邊啲牌子比較好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想睇下巴絲們有冇好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 洗衣乾衣機<br />\n2. 電磁爐<br />\n3. 微波爐<br />\n4. 抽油煙機<br />\n5. 雪櫃<br />\n<br />\nBudget大約每件4000 - 7000蚊左右<br />\n求介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：真係想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951b53bd83adb32fea67b5dff8165596c57a14cc","tid":128381,"uid":30324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18b71cff47526cf1b20d8c7b5c6672845aec783","tid":128381,"uid":30324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dceb7ac50c00954f3fa7aeb894abbfb2b1dc0cd","tid":128381,"uid":30324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86c89b0dd05cefeb24e8cddb40509539950b2a7","tid":128381,"uid":30324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b0b463255cb4a754b0d81427343ea8a5130aff","tid":128381,"uid":30324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi